ticipant GUI as GUI Manager\n    participant Console as ConsoleWidget\n\n    CLI->>App: execute Command.action()\n    App->>GUI: gui()\n    GUI->>Console: widget('console').clear()\n    Console->>Console: clear lines_, set updateText_, invalidate()\n    Console->>GUI: render/update display\n```\n\n</details>\n\n<!-- walkthrough_end -->\n\n\n<!-- pre_merge_checks_walkthrough_start -->\n\n<details>\n<summary>🚥 Pre-merge checks | ✅ 4</summary>\n\n<details>\n<summary>✅ Passed checks (4 passed)</summary>\n\n|               Check name              | Status   | Explanation                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |\n| :-----------------------------------: | :------- | :------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |\n|              Title check              | ✅ Passed | The title 'CLI: Add `clear` command to clear console output' directly and clearly summarizes the main change—adding a new clear command to the CLI.                                                                                                                 |\n|           Description check           | ✅ Passed | The description is directly related to the changeset, explaining the motivation for the clear command and detailing the implementation and test plan.                                                                                                               |\n|           Docstring Coverage          | ✅ Passed | No functions found in the changed files to evaluate docstring coverage. Skipping docstring coverage check.                                                                     